# Phase F：五折 DEP/HC 难度对比

## 目标

判断 DEP fold0 是否是孤立异常，还是 DEP 组普遍难。

## 输出

```text
outputs/group_analysis/group_fold_difficulty_matrix.csv
```

## 字段

| fold | dep_ba | hc_ba | dep_hc_gap | dep_n_subjects | hc_n_subjects |
| ---- | -----: | ----: | ---------: | -------------: | ------------: |

## 判断

如果只有 fold0 DEP 异常低：

```text
DEP fold0 may be fold-specific hard split.
```

如果 DEP 所有 fold 都低：

```text
DEP group is globally harder.
```

如果 DEP 某些 fold 高、某些 fold 低：

```text
DEP difficulty is subject-dependent rather than purely group-dependent.
```

